Package: sift
Type: Package
Title: Fuzzily search dataframe columns, labels, and factor levels to find variables
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Desi Quintans
Maintainer: Desi Quintans <science@desiquintans.com>
Description: Fuzzily search dataframe column names, labels, and factor levels to find
    which columns contain the variables you need. Designed for use with large 
    dataframes that can span thousands of columns and millions of rows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
    cli,
    fastdigest
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
